<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Web相关 - 分类 - w23ta0's blog</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/web%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/</link><description>You got a dream, you gotta protect it.</description><generator>Hugo 0.145.0 &amp; FixIt v0.3.16</generator><language>zh-cn</language><managingEditor>tom920wt@hotmail.com (w23ta0)</managingEditor><webMaster>tom920wt@hotmail.com (w23ta0)</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 11:23:13 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/web%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>使用 CSS 实现标题自动编号</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20151023-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-css-%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E7%BC%96%E5%8F%B7/</link><pubDate>Fri, 23 Oct 2015 18:27:00 +0000</pubDate><author>tom920wt@hotmail.com (w23ta0)</author><guid>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20151023-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-css-%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E7%BC%96%E5%8F%B7/</guid><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/web%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/">Web相关</category><description>&lt;p>近几天在学习 HTML5 与 CSS3 时，偶然看到了 CSS 中自动为标题添加编号的特性。仔细阅读过 W3Schools 上提供的文档之后，试验了一下，确实非常好用。从此不需再花费精力校对标题编号，可以将时间集中到真正需要做的事情，也避免了手动编号出错的窘态。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>这篇博文整理了我搜集的相关知识点，方便希望详细了解的人查看。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="涉及内容" class="heading-element">&lt;span>涉及内容&lt;/span>
 &lt;a href="#%e6%b6%89%e5%8f%8a%e5%86%85%e5%ae%b9" class="heading-mark">
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true">&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z">&lt;/path>&lt;/svg>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>首先介绍一下本文涉及到的相关 CSS 知识点。其中用到的 CSS 伪元素和属性皆基于 CSS2.1 标准，所以基本不需要担心浏览器的兼容性问题。如果你对此还不够放心，可以在不同浏览器中打开文末给出的样例进行测试。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>LoadRunner 11 安装及破解</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20150820-loadrunner-11-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%8F%8A%E7%A0%B4%E8%A7%A3/</link><pubDate>Thu, 20 Aug 2015 13:14:53 +0000</pubDate><author>tom920wt@hotmail.com (w23ta0)</author><guid>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20150820-loadrunner-11-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%8F%8A%E7%A0%B4%E8%A7%A3/</guid><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/web%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/">Web相关</category><description>&lt;h2 id="前提条件" class="heading-element">&lt;span>前提条件&lt;/span>
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e6%8f%90%e6%9d%a1%e4%bb%b6" class="heading-mark">
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true">&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z">&lt;/path>&lt;/svg>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>内存：2G，硬盘空闲空间10G，安装完成后实际只占不到2G
支持winXP SP3;32位与64位win7浏览器支持IE6-8,IE9,firefox3
若以前安装过LoadRunner,则将其卸载。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Apache访问日志分析</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20150812-apache%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90/</link><pubDate>Wed, 12 Aug 2015 17:03:37 +0000</pubDate><author>tom920wt@hotmail.com (w23ta0)</author><guid>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20150812-apache%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90/</guid><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/web%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/">Web相关</category><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/apache/">Apache</category><description>&lt;p>当前WEB服务器中联接次数最多的ip地址&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">$ netstat -ntu &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span>awk &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;{print $5}&amp;#39;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span>sort &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span> uniq -c&lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span> sort -nr&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>查看日志中访问次数最多的前10个IP&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">$ cat access.log &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span>cut -d &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39; &amp;#39;&lt;/span> -f &lt;span class="m">1&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span>sort &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span>uniq -c &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span> sort -nr &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span> awk &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;{print $0 }&amp;#39;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span> head -n &lt;span class="m">10&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span>less&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>查看日志中出现100次以上的IP&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">$ cat access.log &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span>cut -d &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39; &amp;#39;&lt;/span> -f &lt;span class="m">1&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span>sort &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span>uniq -c &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span> awk &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;{if ($1 &amp;gt; 100) print $0}&amp;#39;&lt;/span>｜sort -nr &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span>less&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>查看最近访问量最高的文件&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">$ cat access.log &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span>tail -10000&lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span>awk &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;{print $7}&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span>sort&lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span>uniq -c&lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span>sort -nr&lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span>less&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>查看日志中访问超过100次的页面&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">$ cat access.log &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span> cut -d &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39; &amp;#39;&lt;/span> -f &lt;span class="m">7&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span> sort &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span>uniq -c &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span> awk &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;{if ($1 &amp;gt; 100) print $0}&amp;#39;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span> less&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>统计某url，一天的访问次数&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Nginx重定向&amp;静动资源分离</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20150624-nginx%E9%87%8D%E5%AE%9A%E5%90%91%E9%9D%99%E5%8A%A8%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E5%88%86%E7%A6%BB/</link><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2015 13:05:51 +0000</pubDate><author>tom920wt@hotmail.com (w23ta0)</author><guid>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20150624-nginx%E9%87%8D%E5%AE%9A%E5%90%91%E9%9D%99%E5%8A%A8%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E5%88%86%E7%A6%BB/</guid><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/web%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/">Web相关</category><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/nginx/">Nginx</category><description>&lt;h2 id="域名重写" class="heading-element">&lt;span>域名重写&lt;/span>
 &lt;a href="#%e5%9f%9f%e5%90%8d%e9%87%8d%e5%86%99" class="heading-mark">
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true">&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z">&lt;/path>&lt;/svg>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>我们可以在同一个server中绑定域名www.example.com和example.com两个域名：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-nginx" data-lang="nginx">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">server&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="kn">listen&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">80&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="kn">server_name&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">example.com&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">www.example.com&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>但是这样对我们的SEO非常不利，我们需要使用301（rewrite）将一个域名重定向到另一个，比如将example重定向到www.example.com。这里要依赖于正则表达式的分组（使用$1来引用分组）。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Nginx中的upstream轮询机制介绍</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20150614-nginx%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84upstream%E8%BD%AE%E8%AF%A2%E6%9C%BA%E5%88%B6%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D/</link><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jun 2015 13:03:23 +0000</pubDate><author>tom920wt@hotmail.com (w23ta0)</author><guid>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20150614-nginx%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84upstream%E8%BD%AE%E8%AF%A2%E6%9C%BA%E5%88%B6%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D/</guid><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/web%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/">Web相关</category><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/nginx/">Nginx</category><description>&lt;p>Nginx中upstream有以下几种方式：&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>轮询(weight=1)&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;p>默认选项，当weight不指定时，各服务器weight相同，
每个请求按时间顺序逐一分配到不同的后端服务器，如果后端服务器down掉，能自动剔除。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-nginx" data-lang="nginx">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">upstream&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">bakend&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="kn">server&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">192&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">.168.1.10&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="kn">server&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">192&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">.168.1.11&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;ol start="2">
&lt;li>weight&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;p>指定轮询几率，weight和访问比率成正比，用于后端服务器性能不均的情况。
如果后端服务器down掉，能自动剔除。
比如下面配置，则1.11服务器的访问量为1.10服务器的两倍。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>.htaccess实现网页Gzip压缩</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20120824-.htaccess%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E7%BD%91%E9%A1%B5gzip%E5%8E%8B%E7%BC%A9/</link><pubDate>Fri, 24 Aug 2012 09:41:47 +0000</pubDate><author>tom920wt@hotmail.com (w23ta0)</author><guid>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20120824-.htaccess%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E7%BD%91%E9%A1%B5gzip%E5%8E%8B%E7%BC%A9/</guid><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/web%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/">Web相关</category><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/nginx/">Nginx</category><description>&lt;p>最近抽出了一点时间，研究了使用.htaccess 开启网页gzip压缩的问题。
大家都知道网页打开速度与dns，服务器，页面代码，网站结构，统统都相关。
网页压缩的问题。因为本人的大部分网站都是PHP的，所以，基本需要.htaccess来解决。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>在.htaccess文件中请加入以下代码即可：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">11
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">12
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">13
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">14
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">15
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">16
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">17
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">18
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">19
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">20
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">21
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">22
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">23
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">24
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">25
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">26
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">27
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">28
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">29
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">30
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">31
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">32
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">33
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">34
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">35
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-php" data-lang="php">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="o">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">IfModule&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">mod_deflate&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">c&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
